bcd, caesar, canfield, cfscores, cribbage, go-fish, gomoku,
hunt, mille, mpoly, morse, number, phantasia, pig, pom, ppt, primes,
quiz, rain, random, robots, rot13, sail, snake, snscore, teachgammon,
